OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny low cloud clearing this
OL,6,Fmorning. Another dry and sunny day for
OL,7,Fmuch of the region, although some
OL,8,Fcloud and a few spots of rain may move
OL,9,Finto Cumbria during the afternoon.
OL,10,FFeeling very warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA few spots of rain possible
OL,13,Fin Cumbria this evening, otherwise a
OL,14,Fdry night across the region. Some
OL,15,Fpatches of low cloud may form, and
OL,16,Fstaying warm.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FAny low cloud lifting and
OL,19,Fbreaking to give another warm and
OL,20,Fsunny day. A brisk breeze picking up
OL,21,Finto the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
