OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FStaying dry, sunny and settled through
OL,7,Fthe outlook and staying very warm.
OL,8,FWinds gradually easing for everyone
OL,9,Fafter the weekend.
